  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-07-01",
    "date": "2022-04-19T10:49:44Z",
    "text": "Fair COLA for Seniors Act\n\nThis bill bases cost-of-living adjustments for certain benefits available through federal and military retirement programs, Social Security, and specified programs for veterans on a price index that tracks the spending patterns of older consumers. The Bureau of Labor Statistics of the Department of Labor must publish that price index on a monthly basis."
  },
